    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：939480246</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《奶茶店大亨》——是时候拥有你命中注定的那家奶茶店啦！在这里，你不仅可以亲手制作奶茶，还能脑洞大开发明配方，甚至把你的小店打造成这条街最靓的奶茶空间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/5bdd7ce3df4405185ba3c2cb9af71f67.avif?t=1770397594\" width=744 height=184 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/5847da352b639ceb924f7036301a68c9.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/5847da352b639ceb924f7036301a68c9.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/5847da352b639ceb924f7036301a68c9.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✧ 你，就是奶茶店的天选之人 ✧<br>作为奶茶店的店主，一手包办点单、制作、打包一条龙服务！记住，客人的耐心比珍珠还容易沉底，你的手速将决定小店是五星好评还是差评轰炸～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/b48ef5d5da8ce7c476665eb18127ecab.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/b48ef5d5da8ce7c476665eb18127ecab.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/b48ef5d5da8ce7c476665eb18127ecab.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🛒 备料如备战，开店如开挂 🛒<br>提前囤好茶、奶、糖、珍珠，别等客人排到门口才想起——哎呀，椰果用完了！按照你的节奏点击“开始营业”，然后……接受疯狂点击的洗礼吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/14c9bdc7122258ae13ffde18211e4c9e.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/14c9bdc7122258ae13ffde18211e4c9e.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/14c9bdc7122258ae13ffde18211e4c9e.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🧪奶茶实验室正式启动 🧪<br>研究新配方，调配神秘口味！是芋泥波波霸气登场，还是薄荷咖啡异军突起？全由你说了算！来啊，用上百种原料调配出属于你的“暗黑”特饮！芒果混咖啡？奶盖配辣椒？只要敢想，没有调不出的味道！完成小游戏，解锁隐藏潜力，每一杯奶茶都可能成为朋友圈爆款～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/0d4c3dda11fbdce76d4e16d7df82e262.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/0d4c3dda11fbdce76d4e16d7df82e262.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/0d4c3dda11fbdce76d4e16d7df82e262.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>🏡 装修自由，风格由你 🏡<br>从地板到吊灯，从选择店面布局到挑选装饰品，每一步都需要你的独特眼光与创意！把小店打造成网红打卡地，让客人不仅来喝奶茶，还赖着不走聊人生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/1927c3dc63e6b1decc8a92bd32eb41b5.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/1927c3dc63e6b1decc8a92bd32eb41b5.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/1927c3dc63e6b1decc8a92bd32eb41b5.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👥奶茶导师来帮你，美食挑战在等你 👥<br>友善的NPC会化身奶茶导师，教你从小白进阶成摇茶大师；而挑剔的美食家则会甩出高难度订单——接受挑战，赢取稀有食材，让你的菜单永远领先版本！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/2bd46cf4b2ff2f5385268b83ebb69ad5.poster.avif?t=1770397594\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/2bd46cf4b2ff2f5385268b83ebb69ad5.webm?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334520/extras/2bd46cf4b2ff2f5385268b83ebb69ad5.mp4?t=1770397594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️叔叔带配方，环球跑断腿 🗺️<br>资助你那位热爱冒险的叔叔满世界找茶！去秘境寻找神秘小料？还是去高原寻找极品牛奶？只为追寻传说中“喝了会发光”的终极配方～记得多给他打钱，毕竟……机票挺贵的。</p>",
